name: Gophers Say! GopherCon EU Edition (Go Time #241)
summary: Our award winning worthy survey game show is back, this time Mat Ryer hosts it live on stage at GopherCon Europe 2022! Go Time’s Natalie Pistunovich joins forces with Ronna Steinberg &amp; Robert Burke to battle it out  with V Körbes, Tamir Bahar &amp; Konrad Richie.
